  "texts": [
    "SciEval serves as an essential benchmarking tool aimed at measuring artificial intelligence (AI) developments.",
    "The benchmark consists of a variety of tasks derived from academic science evaluations, providing a detailed assessment of LLMs' capabilities in handling scientific questions and challenges.",
    "This benchmark offers educators a valuable means to evaluate how well LLMs can support science teaching and learning.",
    "Insights from SciEval enable teachers to thoughtfully integrate AI into their curriculum, using AI strengths (or weaknesses) to enhance students' grasp of scientific concepts.",
    "At the same time, it helps educators understand the limitations of AI, ensuring they can guide students in areas where human insight remains indispensable."
